pl.myrecipebasket.model

Class Category

  • java.lang.Object
    • pl.myrecipebasket.model.Category
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    @Entity
public class Category
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Object Category represents a category of meals, dishes, food occasions etc., to which a Recipe can be assigned to and by which a Recipe can be described by.

    A Category has:
    • cName - category name (e.g. Lunch, Dinner, Vegetarian)
    • cType - category type (USER_DEFINED, PRE_DEFINED)
    • cDescription - category description
    • cRecipes - list of Recipes that are assigned to this Category
    See Also:
    Recipe, CategoryType, Serialized Form
